Subject: ALSA: hda - Check "beep" hint
Patch-mainline: 
References: 

Check the hint "beep" in snd_hda_attach_beep_device() to avoid the beep
device creation if user doesn't want.

Signed-off-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

